Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "google_storage_bucket" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name     = "<example_resource_name>"
  location = "<LOCATION>"

  retention_policy {
    retention_period = 86400         # Required: enable a retention policy (1 day)
    is_locked        = true          # CRITICAL: locks the retention policy (Bucket Lock) to pass the check
  }
}
```
